unt</a><span><p>writes fiction and non-fiction. His books include <a href="https://nickhuntscrutiny.com/where-the-wild-winds-are/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>Where the Wild Winds Are</em></a> (2017), <a href="https://nickhuntscrutiny.com/outlandish/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>Outlandish</em></a> (2021) and the novel <a href="https://nickhuntscrutiny.com/red-smoking-mirror-2/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>Red Smoking Mirror</em></a> (2023). He also writes for <em>The Guardian</em> and <em>Perspective</em>, among others, and co-directs the <a href="https://dark-mountain.net/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener">Dark Mountain Project</a>. He lives in Bristol, UK.</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-3ddd79c0-9 eACYrZ"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/cameron-allan-mckean" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 jexetL">Cameron Allan McKean</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-114c07c9-0 iNdsQY"><span>5,400<!-- --> words</span><span class="sc-114c07c9-2 hRWhru"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height="17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span>Save</span></span></div><br/><div class="sc-50e6fb3a-1 jUPTLs"><a class="sc-45649ee9-0 fOpabg sc-50e6fb3a-0 gZdfWA" href="/syndication?article_slug=on-the-intangible-border-of-the-kogis-sacred-mountains&amp;article_name=A%20glimpse%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20heart&amp;author=Nick%20Hunt&amp;date=1%20December%202023"><span class="sc-45649ee9-1 cacrwE">Syndicate this <!-- -->essay</span></a></div><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 bSqqMf sc-3ddd79c0-13 kNGStK"><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 bSqqMf"><div><br/></div><div class="sc-531dc212-0 gowMUU"><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-email" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6zm-2 0l-8 5-8-5h16zm0 12H4V8l8 5 8-5v10z"></path></svg><span class="sc-531dc212-2 gjonPf">Email</span></div><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-531dc212-2 gjonPf">Save</span></div><div><svg viewBox="0 0 256 209" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-twitter" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M256,25.4500259 C246.580841,29.6272672 236.458451,32.4504868 225.834156,33.7202333 C236.678503,27.2198053 245.00583,16.9269929 248.927437,4.66307685 C238.779765,10.6812633 227.539325,15.0523376 215.57599,17.408298 C205.994835,7.2006971 192.34506,0.822 177.239197,0.822 C148.232605,0.822 124.716076,24.3375931 124.716076,53.3423116 C124.716076,57.4586875 125.181462,61.4673784 126.076652,65.3112644 C82.4258385,63.1210453 43.7257252,42.211429 17.821398,10.4359288 C13.3005011,18.1929938 10.710443,27.2151234 10.710443,36.8402889 C10.710443,55.061526 19.9835254,71.1374907 34.0762135,80.5557137 C25.4660961,80.2832239 17.3681846,77.9207088 10.2862577,73.9869292 C10.2825122,74.2060448 10.2825122,74.4260967 10.2825122,74.647085 C10.2825122,100.094453 28.3867003,121.322443 52.413563,126.14673 C48.0059695,127.347184 43.3661509,127.988612 38.5755734,127.988612 C35.1914554,127.988612 31.9009766,127.659938 28.694773,127.046602 C35.3777973,147.913145 54.7742053,163.097665 77.7569918,163.52185 C59.7820257,177.607983 37.1354036,186.004604 12.5289